sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Buyer
    participant FE as Frontend (React)
    participant API as Backend API (FastAPI)
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant Product as Product Service
    participant Cart as Cart/Order Service
    participant DB as MySQL DB
    participant Notify as Notification Service

    Buyer->>FE: Login(email, password)
    FE->>API: POST /auth/login
    API->>Auth: login_user(...)
    Auth->>DB: SELECT user by email
    DB-->>Auth: user row
    Auth-->>API: auth success + user
    API-->>FE: 200 OK

    Buyer->>FE: Browse marketplace
    FE->>API: GET /products/marketplace
    API->>Product: get_all_products_for_marketplace()
    Product->>DB: SELECT active approved products
    DB-->>Product: product list
    Product-->>API: products
    API-->>FE: 200 OK + products

    Buyer->>FE: Add item to cart
    FE->>API: POST /cart/add
    API->>Cart: add_to_cart(buyer_id, product_id, qty)
    Cart->>DB: SELECT product availability
    DB-->>Cart: available_quantity
    Cart->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE cart_items
    DB-->>Cart: success
    Cart-->>API: Added to cart
    API-->>FE: 200 OK

    Buyer->>FE: Checkout(COD/ONLINE)
    FE->>API: POST /cart/checkout
    API->>Cart: checkout(buyer_id, payment_method)
    Cart->>DB: SELECT cart + product details
    DB-->>Cart: cart rows

    alt Payment method = ONLINE
        Cart->>DB: INSERT orders(payment_status=PAID, transaction_id)
    else Payment method = COD
        Cart->>DB: INSERT orders(payment_status=PENDING)
    end

    Cart->>DB: UPDATE products.available_quantity
    Cart->>DB: DELETE buyer cart_items
    DB-->>Cart: committed
    Cart->>Notify: send_order_confirmation_email(...)
    Notify-->>Cart: sent
    Cart-->>API: order_ids + summary
    API-->>FE: 200 OK + confirmation
    FE-->>Buyer: Show order confirmation
